recipes.title: Baileys mini loafs
recipes.instructions: Preheat oven to 350 F. Grease and flour loaf pan. I used a mini loaf pan but you can use a large one.In a bowl mix eggs, oil, baileys, milk and sugar. Add flours, baking powder and cacao nibs and incorporate well.Place mixture on the prepared pan and fill 3/4 of the way and bake for 25-30 minutes or until a tester comes out clean (If using a large baking loaf pan you will need at least 40 minutes of baking time)Remove from the oven and cool on the pan for about 15-20 minutes before removing from the pan.

steps.step: Preheat oven to 350 F. Grease and flour loaf pan. I used a mini loaf pan but you can use a large one.In a bowl mix eggs, oil, baileys, milk and sugar.
Add flours, baking powder and cacao nibs and incorporate well.

Place mixture on the prepared pan and fill 3/4 of the way and bake for 25-30 minutes or until a tester comes out clean (If using a large baking loaf pan you will need at least 40 minutes of baking time)
Remove from the oven and cool on the pan for about 15-20 minutes before removing from the pan.
